name: BlockChain Barcodes 01 - We're Gonna Make It
description: BlockChain Barcodes are a collection of phrases common in our community that have been translated from an ASCI string into binary and then represented as a Code 128 Standard barcode that can be read with a barcode scanning app. Included in the footer is the original string to juxtapose the digitization of the human experience and consider the abstraction of data into art. Provided as part of the OBJKT4OBJKT event
